    <item>
      <title>342.Power of Four</title>
      <link>http://changcui.cc/posts/leetcode-342/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2019 00:08:18 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://changcui.cc/posts/leetcode-342/</guid>
      <description>class Solution { public: bool isPowerOfFour(int num) { return (num &amp;gt; 0) &amp;amp;&amp;amp; !(num &amp;amp; (num - 1)) &amp;amp;&amp;amp; (num &amp;amp; 0x55555555) == num; } }; </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>231.Power of Two</title>
      <link>http://changcui.cc/posts/leetcode-231/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2019 00:03:02 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://changcui.cc/posts/leetcode-231/</guid>
      <description>class Solution { public: bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) { return (n &amp;gt; 0) &amp;amp;&amp;amp; !(n &amp;amp; (n - 1)); } }; </description>
